=====================================================

Sometimes, like in R, it is convenient to paste c: and change it to
c:/. This can be accomplished by modifying the
`auto-indent-after-yank-hook'.

The code for changing the paths is as follows:

(defun kicker-ess-fix-path (beg end) "Fixes ess path" (save-restriction
(save-excursion (narrow-to-region beg end) (goto-char (point-min))
(when (looking-at "[A-Z]:\\") (while (search-forward "\" nil t)
(replace-match "/"))))))

(defun kicker-ess-turn-on-fix-path () (interactive) (when (string= "S"
ess-language) (add-hook 'auto-indent-after-yank-hook
